<h2>Think like a programmer</h2><br>
<b>1) proceural thinking</b><br><br>
Take a big problem and break the solution into few steps.<br><br>
<b>2) Abstract thinking</b><br><br>
Abstract thinking unable to presant physically.It is related to symbolic thinking,which uses the substitution of a symbol for an object or idea.<br><br>
<b>3) Systematic Debugging</b><br><br>
Systematicaly identifying the problem and then track down all the possible causes untill find the problem.<br><br>
<b>4) Technologycal Empathy</b><br><br>
How computer sees things and think about it in that way.<br><br>
<b>5) Systems Thinking</b><br><br>
